" when on a word, change 'word' to '#{word}' (usefull for ruby)

" Leader a , with a like accolade
nnoremap <Leader>sa diwi#{<C-r>"}<ESC>
nnoremap <Leader>sA diWi#{<C-r>"}<ESC>

nnoremap <Leader>s' diwi'<C-r>"'<ESC>
nnoremap <Leader>s' diWi'<C-r>"'<ESC>

nnoremap <Leader>s" diwi"<C-r>""<ESC>
nnoremap <Leader>s" diWi"<C-r>""<ESC>
